  <brief_title>Does Capsulectomy, Performed in Total Hip Arthroplasty With a Direct Anterior Approach Cause Knee Extension Strength Loss?</brief_title>
  <official_title>Does Capsulectomy, Performed in Total Hip Arthroplasty With a Direct Anterior Approach Cause Knee Extension Strength Loss?</official_title>
